Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:21.42,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}现在 立刻 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:24.51,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}穿越阴霾 来到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:30.44,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只为守护心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.77,0:01:42.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}那一刻 齿轮悄悄转动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:55.61,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}将新的命运 带到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.14,0:01:58.62,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}恋心 生根发芽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.73,0:02:01.40,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}思念 深藏心底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:09.31,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}在眼神交汇的瞬间 抛却掩饰与矜持
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:15.28,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}心愿只此一件 拥有坚不可摧的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:21.11,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}无论在怎样的试炼中倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.52,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}现在 立刻 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:26.67,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}再一次 重新站起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:29.84,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}请稍带片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:35.91,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}正是你赐予了我 将软弱一刀两断的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:40.14,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,600)}{\blur2)}Justice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:36.12,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}静静地 静静地 扮在你身边 化身一阵微风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:43.18,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只为把你沮丧的泪水  轻轻吹干
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.83,0:22:50.23,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}口袋中 那小小的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:56.96,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只盼你开怀一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}跑吧 跑吧 不断加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:05.57,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}即使发生不开心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.73,0:23:08.97,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}也要在这条路上继续奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.23,0:23:13.88,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}前方的地图 早已印在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:17.66,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}明天是个 happy day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:25.04,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,600)}{\blur2)}奇迹般闪耀的happy day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.99,0:00:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要当骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汉尼拔尔大叔知道肯定吓得腿软
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有言在先 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这座城市和这里的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.09,0:00:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想保护他们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家永远面带笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽兹的话 一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.95,0:00:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打一把属于我的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我还…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我将成为骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克会成为刀匠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人一起守护这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.59,0:00:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这主意不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早饭要凉了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一晃三年了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天休息吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 难得有时间想锻炼一下身体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:47.14,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,500)}{\blur2}面庞 -Lisa-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二头肌还需要再强壮一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 可悲可叹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的女孩子休息日想着增加肌肉？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想自己的女儿更像个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妈妈太奢望了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就找不到一位能陪你度过假日的男士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才没呢 那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 原来有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子真看不出…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个什么样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点冷淡 相貌还算不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔 为塞西莉准备衣裳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣裳？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈把自己的借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好打扮一下 去邀请那位先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我 阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你摸哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没心理准备 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪种比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 问我也没用喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道她的喜好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 还真没问过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般我想应该是白花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如…这朵怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这朵也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能让任何人看到！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我非得穿成这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住 关键是用色诱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色 诱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功捕获男人的心之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许回家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不去自找没趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说干脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过夜 如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙根本没把我当女人看待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要和卢克那种人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这身打扮的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛮可爱的 今天不当班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好 有件事拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位姑娘想找人修短剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她去卢克那里好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那倒不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫埃尔莎 劳烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮完佣人又扮女装吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是字面的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没其他想说的了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我这么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开个玩笑 有事快说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给卢克带来位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫埃尔莎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说想找人修理短剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把剑对我很重要 能想办法修好它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Misericordia（怜悯）吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑芯断了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法修理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么让我稍许保养一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事得出门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要向你汇报…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你也来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…哪里有？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没走出几里地 就在路上绊倒十几次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你紧张什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不许胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算和男人单独相处 我怎么可能紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天还和男子团员一起市内巡逻来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吃了你 别这么拘谨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又捉弄人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真像极了某个人 喜欢逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我像谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这是去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这些花是干什么用的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你去哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩都有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 因为我的缘故…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 原本就打算这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和他一起去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成和莉萨吵嘴了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没吵什么嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么问？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很能干 没有什么不满
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实想过 这样下去好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久前 买了顶帽子给她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停地道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:10:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才察觉 我迄今为止连这点小事都没有为她做过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概还有许多我没有察觉的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她继续留在身边是否合适
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她或许也有属于自己的生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉萨信任你 也愿意跟着你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是 莉萨应该也想留在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉萨真的是出于自己的意愿留在我身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想莉萨怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保…护
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是为了保护她 什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都能忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把短剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何给人悲伤的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛如在哭泣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚 隐隐约约
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把短剑 Misericordia的意思是慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专门用来杀死受伤而无法可医的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了让他们解脱？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把剑是某位骑士奔赴战场前赠与爱女的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发誓就算奄奄一息也会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时宁愿死在深爱的女儿手里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 骑士回来时…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本该死的人活了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该死的人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的一切都被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这把短剑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修复裂痕的话 或许就能治愈过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 果真就算修好裂痕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法治愈过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉萨？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是丽兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽兹{\fnsimhei}·{\r}奥克伍德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没能保护好的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽兹{\fnsimhei}·{\r}奥克伍德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没能保护好的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能保护好？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店名是丽兹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个人的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽兹和我青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前 被瓦尔巴尼尔杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你说被谁杀了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦尔巴尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦尔巴尼尔…那可是传说中的人外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙才不是什么传说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦尔巴尼尔确实存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亲眼所见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 它还在那里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 我和丽兹跟着父亲去了锻造屋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 老爸这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把我赶出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没办法 卢克还是学徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我也知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样就满足了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么满足不满足的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是卢克为我打的第一把刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是试验作品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 送给我劣质品？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么劣质品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我现有技术下打出的最好水准
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续练习的话 应该还能打出更好的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 玉钢也不便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又长进了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为每天都在练习
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点模样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赖皮 自己一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹别扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成为骑士后 会保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保护城里的大伙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便也保护卢克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感动到要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 尽快能够独当一面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打出最棒的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里往前有个洞穴 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往弗雷亚火山的那个洞穴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规定禁止入内的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是连靠近都不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非害怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说谁害怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太傻了 我们为了寻找乐趣越走越深
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到…遇见了它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽兹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽兹死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来找我们的父亲也被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能眼睁睁看着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死光了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我幸存
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了 抱歉说给你听又长又乏味的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么带我来？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只觉得有几分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽兹和你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我的技术只能做到这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的这么认为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能舍弃过去与经历 只为现在而活？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…这么相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉进展顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人放心不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克 你有太多谜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还几乎一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为对你多一些了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能缩短彼此之间的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在却害怕去了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢…卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽兹…你爱着她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是“爱过”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽兹已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊 找到瓦尔巴尼尔的踪迹了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 您还记得它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座城市中有人继承了瓦尔巴尼尔的血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那个黑衣男子 难以令人信任…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瓦尔巴尼尔杀死了埃尔莎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪恶滔天的瓦尔巴尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何都要为埃尔莎报仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨 恨之入骨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 您还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦尔巴尼尔在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉 今天我遇见…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 明天再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下大了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟们明明说了今天不下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的倾盆大雨反而让人舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来时也没和塞西莉一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉萨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在那里吗 瓦尔巴尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你召唤我来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕 瓦尔巴尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魔剑 操纵雷电的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里别动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.48,0:21:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话少说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦尔巴尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:21:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉萨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧 瓦尔巴尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉萨！
